var book = {
	"name": "Song of Solomon",
	"numChapters": 8,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The Song of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17539A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17539A\"></sup>Songs, which is Solomon's.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Let him kiss me with the kisses of his mouth!For your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17540B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17540B\"></sup>love is better than wine;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17541C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17541C\"></sup>anointing oils are fragrant;your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17541D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17541D\"></sup>name is oil poured out;therefore virgins love you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17542E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17542E\"></sup>Draw me after you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17542F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17542F\"></sup>let us run.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17542G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17542G\"></sup>The king has brought me into his chambers.We will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17542H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17542H\"></sup>exult and rejoice in you;we will extol <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17542I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17542I\"></sup>your love more than wine;rightly do they love you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I am very dark, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17543J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17543J\"></sup>lovely,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17543K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17543K\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem,like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17543L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17543L\"></sup>the tents of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17543M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17543M\"></sup>Kedar,like the curtains of Solomon.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not gaze at me because I am dark,because the sun has looked upon me.My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17544N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17544N\"></sup>mother's sons were angry with me;they made me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17544O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17544O\"></sup>keeper of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17544P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17544P\"></sup>the vineyards,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17544Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17544Q\"></sup>my own vineyard I have not kept!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Tell me, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17545R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17545R\"></sup>whom my soul loves,where you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17545S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17545S\"></sup>pasture your flock,where you make it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17545T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17545T\"></sup>lie down at noon;for why should I be like one who veils herselfbeside the flocks of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17545U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17545U\"></sup>companions?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If you do not know,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17546V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17546V\"></sup>most beautiful among women,follow in the tracks of the flock,and pasture your young goatsbeside the shepherds' tents.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I compare you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17547W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17547W\"></sup>my love,to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17547X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17547X\"></sup>a mare among Pharaoh's chariots.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17548Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17548Y\"></sup>Your cheeks are lovely with ornaments,your neck with strings of jewels.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>We will make for you ornaments of gold,studded with silver.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>While <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17550Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17550Z\"></sup>the king was on his couch,my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17550AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17550AA\"></sup>nard gave forth its fragrance.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>My beloved is to me a sachet of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17551AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17551AB\"></sup>myrrhthat lies between my breasts.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>My beloved is to me a cluster of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17552AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17552AC\"></sup>henna blossomsin the vineyards of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17552AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17552AD\"></sup>Engedi.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17553AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17553AE\"></sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17553AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17553AF\"></sup>you are beautiful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17553AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17553AG\"></sup>my love;behold, you are beautiful;your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17553AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17553AH\"></sup>eyes are doves.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Behold, you are beautiful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17554AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17554AI\"></sup>my beloved, truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17554AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17554AJ\"></sup>delightful.Our couch is green;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>the beams of our house are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17555AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17555AK\"></sup>cedar;our rafters are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17555AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17555AL\"></sup>pine."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>I am a rose of Sharon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17556A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17556A\"></sup>a lily of the valleys.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>As a lily among brambles,so is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17557B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17557B\"></sup>my love among the young women.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As an apple tree among the trees of the forest,so is my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17558C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17558C\"></sup>beloved among the young men.With great delight I sat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17558D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17558D\"></sup>in his shadow,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17558E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17558E\"></sup>fruit was sweet to my taste.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17559F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17559F\"></sup>brought me to the banqueting house,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17559G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17559G\"></sup>banner over me was love.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Sustain me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17560H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17560H\"></sup>raisins;refresh me with apples,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17560I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17560I\"></sup>for I am sick with love.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17561J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17561J\"></sup>left hand is under my head,and his right hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17561K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17561K\"></sup>embraces me!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17562L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17562L\"></sup>adjure you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17562M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17562M\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem,by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17562N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17562N\"></sup>the gazelles or the does of the field,that you not stir up or awaken loveuntil it pleases.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The voice of my beloved!Behold, he comes,leaping <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17563O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17563O\"></sup>over the mountains,bounding over the hills.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>My beloved is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17564P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17564P\"></sup>a gazelleor a young stag.Behold, there he standsbehind our wall,gazing through the windows,looking through the lattice.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My beloved speaks and says to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17565Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17565Q\"></sup>“Arise, my love, my beautiful one,and come away,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>for behold, the winter is past;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17566R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17566R\"></sup>the rain is over and gone.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17567S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17567S\"></sup>The flowers appear on the earth,the time of singing has come,and the voice of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17567T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17567T\"></sup>the turtledoveis heard in our land.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17568U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17568U\"></sup>The fig tree ripens its figs,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17568V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17568V\"></sup>the vines are in blossom;they give forth fragrance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17568W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17568W\"></sup>Arise, my love, my beautiful one,and come away.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>O my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17569X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17569X\"></sup>dove, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17569Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17569Y\"></sup>clefts of the rock,in the crannies of the cliff,let me see your face,let me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17569Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17569Z\"></sup>hear your voice,for your voice is sweet,and your face is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17569AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17569AA\"></sup>lovely.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Catch <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17570AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17570AB\"></sup>the foxes for us,the little foxesthat spoil the vineyards,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17570AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17570AC\"></sup>for our vineyards are in blossom.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17571AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17571AD\"></sup>My beloved is mine, and I am his;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17571AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17571AE\"></sup>grazes among the lilies.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17572AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17572AF\"></sup>the day breathesand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17572AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17572AG\"></sup>the shadows flee,turn, my beloved, be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17572AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17572AH\"></sup>a gazelleor a young stag on cleft mountains."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>On my bed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17573A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17573A\"></sup>by nightI sought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17573B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17573B\"></sup>him whom my soul loves;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17573C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17573C\"></sup>I sought him, but found him not.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will rise now and go about the city,in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17574D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17574D\"></sup>the streets and in the squares;I will seek <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17574E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17574E\"></sup>him whom my soul loves.I sought him, but found him not.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17575F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17575F\"></sup>The watchmen found meas they went about in the city.“Have you seen him whom my soul loves?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Scarcely had I passed themwhen I found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17576G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17576G\"></sup>him whom my soul loves.I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17576H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17576H\"></sup>held him, and would not let him gountil I had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17576I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17576I\"></sup>brought him into my mother's house,and into the chamber of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17576J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17576J\"></sup>her who conceived me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17577K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17577K\"></sup>I adjure you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17577L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17577L\"></sup>O daughters of Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17577M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17577M\"></sup>by the gazelles or the does of the field,that you not stir up or awaken loveuntil it pleases.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17578N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17578N\"></sup>What is that coming up from the wildernesslike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17578O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17578O\"></sup>columns of smoke,perfumed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17578P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17578P\"></sup>myrrh and frankincense,with all the fragrant powders of a merchant?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, it is the litter of Solomon!Around it are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17579Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17579Q\"></sup>sixty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17579R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17579R\"></sup>mighty men,some of the mighty men of Israel,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>all of them wearing swordsand expert in war,each with his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17580S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17580S\"></sup>sword at his thigh,against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17580T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17580T\"></sup>terror by night.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>King Solomon made himself a carriagefrom the wood of Lebanon.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He made its posts of silver,its back of gold, its seat of purple;its interior was inlaid with loveby <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17582U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17582U\"></sup>the daughters of Jerusalem.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Go out, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17583V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17583V\"></sup>daughters of Zion,and look upon King Solomon,with the crown with which his mother crowned himon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17583W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17583W\"></sup>the day of his wedding,on the day of the gladness of his heart."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17584A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17584A\"></sup>you are beautiful, my love,behold, you are beautiful!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17584B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17584B\"></sup>Your eyes are doves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17584C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17584C\"></sup>behind your veil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17584D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17584D\"></sup>Your hair is like a flock of goatsleaping down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17584E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17584E\"></sup>the slopes of Gilead.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17585F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17585F\"></sup>teeth are like a flock of shorn ewesthat have come up from the washing,all of which bear twins,and not one among them has lost its young.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Your lips are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17586G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17586G\"></sup>a scarlet thread,and your mouth is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17586H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17586H\"></sup>lovely.Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17586I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17586I\"></sup>cheeks are like halves of a pomegranate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17586J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17586J\"></sup>behind your veil.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17587K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17587K\"></sup>neck is like the tower of David,built in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17587L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17587L\"></sup>rows of stone;on it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17587M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17587M\"></sup>hang a thousand shields,all of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17587N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17587N\"></sup>them shields of warriors.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17588O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17588O\"></sup>two breasts are like two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17588P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17588P\"></sup>fawns,twins of a gazelle,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17588Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17588Q\"></sup>graze among the lilies.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17589R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17589R\"></sup>Until the day breathesand the shadows flee,I will go away to the mountain of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17589S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17589S\"></sup>myrrhand the hill of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17589T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17589T\"></sup>frankincense.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17590U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17590U\"></sup>You are altogether beautiful, my love;there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17590V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17590V\"></sup>flaw in you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17591W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17591W\"></sup>Come with me from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17591X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17591X\"></sup>Lebanon, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17591Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17591Y\"></sup>bride;come with me from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17591Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17591Z\"></sup>Lebanon.Depart from the peak of Amana,from the peak of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17591AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17591AA\"></sup>Senir and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17591AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17591AB\"></sup>Hermon,from the dens of lions,from the mountains of leopards.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You have captivated my heart, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17592AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17592AC\"></sup>sister, my bride;you have captivated my heart with one glance of your eyes,with one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17592AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17592AD\"></sup>jewel of your necklace.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>How beautiful is your love, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17593AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17593AE\"></sup>sister, my bride!How much <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17593AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17593AF\"></sup>better is your love than wine,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17593AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17593AG\"></sup>the fragrance of your oils than any spice!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17594AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17594AH\"></sup>lips drip nectar, my bride;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17594AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17594AI\"></sup>honey and milk are under your tongue;the fragrance of your garments is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17594AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17594AJ\"></sup>like the fragrance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17594AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17594AK\"></sup>Lebanon.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A garden locked is my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17595AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17595AL\"></sup>sister, my bride,a spring locked, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17595AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17595AM\"></sup>a fountain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17595AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17595AN\"></sup>sealed.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Your shoots are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17596AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17596AO\"></sup>an orchard of pomegranateswith all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17596AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17596AP\"></sup>choicest fruits,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17596AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17596AQ\"></sup>henna with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17596AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17596AR\"></sup>nard,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>nard and saffron, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17597AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17597AS\"></sup>calamus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17597AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17597AT\"></sup>cinnamon,with all trees of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17597AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17597AU\"></sup>frankincense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17597AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17597AV\"></sup>myrrh and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17597AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17597AW\"></sup>aloes,with all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17597AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17597AX\"></sup>choice spices—",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>a garden fountain, a well of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17598AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17598AY\"></sup>living water,and flowing streams from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17598AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17598AZ\"></sup>Lebanon.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Awake, O north wind,and come, O south wind!Blow upon my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17599BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17599BA\"></sup>garden,let its spices flow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17599BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17599BB\"></sup>Let my beloved come to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17599BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17599BC\"></sup>garden,and eat its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17599BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17599BD\"></sup>choicest fruits."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17600A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17600A\"></sup>came to my garden, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17600B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17600B\"></sup>sister, my bride,I gathered my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17600C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17600C\"></sup>myrrh with my spice,I ate my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17600D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17600D\"></sup>honeycomb with my honey,I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17600E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17600E\"></sup>drank my wine with my milk.Eat, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17600F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17600F\"></sup>friends, drink,and be drunk with love!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I slept, but my heart was awake.A sound! My beloved is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17601G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17601G\"></sup>knocking.“Open to me, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17601H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17601H\"></sup>sister, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17601I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17601I\"></sup>love,my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17601J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17601J\"></sup>dove, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17601K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17601K\"></sup>perfect one,for my head is wet with dew,my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17601L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17601L\"></sup>locks with the drops of the night.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17602M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17602M\"></sup>I had put off my garment;how could I put it on?I had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17602N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17602N\"></sup>bathed my feet;how could I soil them?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>My beloved put his hand to the latch,and my heart was thrilled within me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I arose to open to my beloved,and my hands dripped with myrrh,my fingers with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17604O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17604O\"></sup>liquid myrrh,on the handles of the bolt.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I opened to my beloved,but my beloved had turned and gone.My soul failed me when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17605P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17605P\"></sup>spoke.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17605Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17605Q\"></sup>I sought him, but found him not;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17605R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17605R\"></sup>I called him, but he gave no answer.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17606S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17606S\"></sup>The watchmen found meas they went about in the city;they beat me, they bruised me,they took away my veil,those watchmen of the walls.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17607T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17607T\"></sup>adjure you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17607U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17607U\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem,if you find my beloved,that you tell him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17607V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17607V\"></sup>I am sick with love.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>What is your beloved more than another beloved,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17608W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17608W\"></sup>most beautiful among women?What is your beloved more than another beloved,that you thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17608X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17608X\"></sup>adjure us?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My beloved is radiant and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17609Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17609Y\"></sup>ruddy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17609Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17609Z\"></sup>distinguished among ten thousand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>His head is the finest gold;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17610AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17610AA\"></sup>his locks are wavy,black as a raven.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17611AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17611AB\"></sup>eyes are like dovesbeside streams of water,bathed in milk,sitting beside a full pool.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17612AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17612AC\"></sup>cheeks are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17612AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17612AD\"></sup>beds of spices,mounds of sweet-smelling herbs.His lips are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17612AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17612AE\"></sup>lilies,dripping <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17612AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17612AF\"></sup>liquid myrrh.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>His arms are rods of gold,set with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17613AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17613AG\"></sup>jewels.His body is polished ivory,bedecked with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17613AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17613AH\"></sup>sapphires.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>His legs are alabaster columns,set on bases of gold.His appearance is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17614AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17614AI\"></sup>Lebanon,choice as the cedars.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17615AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17615AJ\"></sup>mouth is most sweet,and he is altogether desirable.This is my beloved and this is my friend,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17615AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17615AK\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Where has your beloved gone,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17616A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17616A\"></sup>most beautiful among women?Where has your beloved turned,that we may seek him with you?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>My beloved has gone down to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17617B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17617B\"></sup>gardento <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17617C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17617C\"></sup>the beds of spices,to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17617D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17617D\"></sup>graze in the gardensand to gather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17617E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17617E\"></sup>lilies.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17618F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17618F\"></sup>I am my beloved's and my beloved is mine;he grazes among the lilies.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You are beautiful as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17619G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17619G\"></sup>Tirzah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17619H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17619H\"></sup>my love,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17619I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17619I\"></sup>lovely as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17619J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17619J\"></sup>Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17619K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17619K\"></sup>awesome as an army with banners.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Turn away your eyes from me,for they overwhelm me—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17620L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17620L\"></sup>Your hair is like a flock of goatsleaping down the slopes of Gilead.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17621M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17621M\"></sup>Your teeth are like a flock of ewesthat have come up from the washing;all of them bear twins;not one among them has lost its young.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17622N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17622N\"></sup>Your cheeks are like halves of a pomegranatebehind your veil.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>There are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17623O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17623O\"></sup>sixty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17623P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17623P\"></sup>queens and eighty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17623Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17623Q\"></sup>concubines,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17623R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17623R\"></sup>virgins without number.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17624S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17624S\"></sup>dove, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17624T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17624T\"></sup>perfect one, is the only one,the only one of her mother,pure to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17624U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17624U\"></sup>her who bore her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17624V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17624V\"></sup>The young women saw her and called her blessed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17624W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17624W\"></sup>the queens and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17624X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17624X\"></sup>concubines also, and they praised her.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17625Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17625Y\"></sup>“Who is this who looks down like the dawn,beautiful as the moon, bright as the sun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17625Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17625Z\"></sup>awesome as an army with banners?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I went down to the nut orchardto look at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17626AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17626AA\"></sup>the blossoms of the valley,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17626AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17626AB\"></sup>to see whether the vines had budded,whether the pomegranates were in bloom.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17627AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17627AC\"></sup>Before I was aware, my desire set meamong <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17627AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17627AD\"></sup>the chariots of my kinsman, a prince.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup> Return, return, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17628AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17628AE\"></sup>Shulammite,return, return, that we may look upon you.Why should you look upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17628AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17628AF\"></sup>the Shulammite,as upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17628AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17628AG\"></sup>a dance before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17628AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17628AH\"></sup>two armies?"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>How beautiful are your feet in sandals,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17629A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17629A\"></sup>noble daughter!Your rounded thighs are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17629B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17629B\"></sup>jewels,the work of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17629C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17629C\"></sup>a master hand.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Your navel is a rounded bowlthat never lacks mixed wine.Your belly is a heap of wheat,encircled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17630D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17630D\"></sup>lilies.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17631E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17631E\"></sup>Your two breasts are like two fawns,twins of a gazelle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17632F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17632F\"></sup>neck is like an ivory tower.Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17632G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17632G\"></sup>eyes are pools in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17632H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17632H\"></sup>Heshbon,by the gate of Bath-rabbim.Your nose is like a tower of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17632I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17632I\"></sup>Lebanon,which looks toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17632J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17632J\"></sup>Damascus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Your head crowns you like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17633K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17633K\"></sup>Carmel,and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17633L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17633L\"></sup>flowing locks are like purple;a king is held captive in the tresses.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17634M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17634M\"></sup>How beautiful and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17634N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17634N\"></sup>pleasant you are,O loved one, with all your delights!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your stature is like a palm tree,and your breasts are like its clusters.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I say I will climb the palm treeand lay hold of its fruit.Oh may your breasts be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17636O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17636O\"></sup>clusters of the vine,and the scent of your breath like apples,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17637P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17637P\"></sup>mouth like the best wine.It goes down smoothly for my beloved,gliding over lips and teeth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17638Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17638Q\"></sup>I am my beloved's,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17638R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17638R\"></sup>and his desire is for me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17639S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17639S\"></sup>Come, my beloved,let us go out into the fieldsand lodge in the villages;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>let us go out early to the vineyards<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17640T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17640T\"></sup>and see whether the vines have budded,whether <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17640U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17640U\"></sup>the grape blossoms have openedand the pomegranates are in bloom.There I will give you my love.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17641V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17641V\"></sup>The mandrakes give forth fragrance,and beside our doors are all choice fruits,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17641W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17641W\"></sup>new as well as old,which I have laid up for you, O my beloved."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Oh that you were like a brother to mewho nursed at my mother's breasts!If I found you outside, I would kiss you,and none would despise me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I would lead you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17643A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17643A\"></sup>bring youinto the house of my mother—she who used to teach me.I would give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17643B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17643B\"></sup>spiced wine to drink,the juice of my pomegranate.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17644C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17644C\"></sup>His left hand is under my head,and his right hand embraces me!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17645D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17645D\"></sup>adjure you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17645E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17645E\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17645F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17645F\"></sup>that you not stir up or awaken loveuntil it pleases.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17646G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17646G\"></sup>Who is that coming up from the wilderness,leaning on her beloved?Under the apple tree I awakened you.There your mother was in labor with you;there she who bore you was in labor.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Set me as a seal upon your heart,as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17647H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17647H\"></sup>a seal upon your arm,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17647I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17647I\"></sup>love is strong as death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17647J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17647J\"></sup>jealousy is fierce as the grave.Its flashes are flashes of fire,the very <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17647K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17647K\"></sup>flame of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Many waters cannot quench love,neither can floods drown it.If a man offered for loveall the wealth of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17648L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17648L\"></sup>house,he would be utterly despised.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We have a little sister,and she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17649M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17649M\"></sup>has no breasts.What shall we do for our sisteron the day when she is spoken for?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If she is a wall,we will build on her a battlement of silver,but if she is a door,we will enclose her with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17650N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17650N\"></sup>boards of cedar.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17651O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17651O\"></sup>I was a wall,and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17651P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17651P\"></sup>breasts were like towers;then I was in his eyesas one who finds peace.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Solomon had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17652Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17652Q\"></sup>a vineyard at Baal-hamon;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17652R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17652R\"></sup>let out the vineyard to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17652S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17652S\"></sup>keepers;each one was to bring for its fruit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17652T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17652T\"></sup>a thousand pieces of silver.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>My vineyard, my very own, is before me;you, O Solomon, may have the thousand,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17653U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17653U\"></sup>the keepers of the fruit two hundred.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17654V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17654V\"></sup>O you who dwell in the gardens,with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17654W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17654W\"></sup>companions listening for your voice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17654X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17654X\"></sup>let me hear it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17655Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17655Y\"></sup>Make haste, my beloved,and be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17655Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17655Z\"></sup>like a gazelleor a young stagon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17655AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17655AA\"></sup>the mountains of spices."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;